                <h1>Baseball legend Hank Aaron visits Duke for naming of summer research program</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/bbf0d70c-a1e3-4515-ad3b-1428341ec8c6.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;A&#x20;Duke-sponsored&#x20;summer&#x20;research&#x20;program&#x20;for&#x20;Durham&#x20;public&#x20;school&#x20;students&#x20;was&#x20;named&#x20;after&#x20;Hank&#x20;Aaron.&amp;nbsp&#x3B;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>A Duke-sponsored summer research program for Durham public school students was named after Hank Aaron.&nbsp;</p>

